{"tid":554831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1歲男童家中昏迷 送院不治","createTime":"2018-02-09T01:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T07:17:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9738a1ceca870cbef0510ef0780738003c0b24d","tid":554831,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:30:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180209/20300413\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180209%2F20300413&d=vtzrkxzLZJEfwH%2FHqlJUrC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=2e3eb4c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180209%2F20300413&h=f0c2ad8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180209/20300413</a><br />\n<br />\n1歲男童家中昏迷<br />\n送院不治<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】大角嘴海弘道帝峰‧皇殿，昨午4時許，一名1歲男童被家人發現於家中昏迷不醒，他事後由救護車送往廣華醫院搶救，惜終告不治。警方正調查男童死因。據悉，男童患有腦積水及肺積水等先天性疾病。"},{"pid":"fe7254fe3d24560f38581a2098fbd969862b5905","tid":554831,"uid":96871,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:32:40.000Z","msg":"可惜呀 咁難得抽到靚首抽"},{"pid":"5a846249df8c10f6c0e8ac457b1e54370ae7e9f3","tid":554831,"uid":44562,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"fe7254fe3d24560f38581a2098fbd969862b5905","tid":554831,"uid":96871,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:32:40.000Z","msg":"可惜呀 咁難得抽到靚首抽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:33:34.000Z","msg":"咁多先天性病都叫靚抽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbe8da5e7bac22682460bb9744372abf8621e66","tid":554831,"uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T01:38:40.000Z","msg":"中水銀毒死"},{"pid":"84e59e2c0ba60db4e72b8a669f22b0612259741b","tid":554831,"uid":6124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a846249df8c10f6c0e8ac457b1e54370ae7e9f3","tid":55